  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb2\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Waiting in line for fuel kills lorry",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "A man waiting in line to get fuel was killed in a lorry collision. The incident took place on Tuesday the 28th, police said.",
        "The man waited in a long queue at a petrol station in Dargah till the night of the 28th and left for home early on Wednesday the 29th.",
        "The deceased has been identified as a 53 year old man from Aluthgama, Dharka.",
        "The lorry driver has been arrested in connection with the accident and police are conducting further investigations"
      ],
